                help
                    The M2-JODY-W5 card combines the maximum performance of the JODY-W5 Wi-Fi 6
                    and Bluetooth 5.3 connectivity module with the flexibility and ease of use
                    of a M.2 card. The card supports all features of the JODY-W5 series modules
                    and is based on the NXP AW611 chipset. M2-JODY-W5 supports Wi‑Fi 6 dual-band
                    single-stream at up to 600 Mbit/s data rate and dual-mode Bluetooth 5.3 Classic
                    and LE including isochronous channels for LE Audio at up to 3 Mbit/s (LE 2 Mbit/s).

                    Detailed information about Jody W5 module you can find on
                    https://www.u-blox.com/en/product/m2-jody-w5-card

